tr/people/bio/lAnzaldua.shtml|title=Leraldo Anzaldua {{!}} Department of Theatre, Drama, and Contemporary Dance|website=www.indiana.edu|language=en|access-date=2017-06-17}}</ref>\n| occupation    = Voice actor, actor, stunt coordinator, ADR director, script writer \n}}\n'''Leraldo Anzaldua''' (born June 22, 1975) is an American voice actor, ADR director, scriptwriter and stunt coordinator who works with [[A.D. Vision|ADV Films]] and [[Seraphim Digital]]/[[Sentai Filmworks]]. He has an [[Master of Fine Arts|M.F.A]]. in acting from the University of Houston. In anime, he is known for providing the English voice of Yuta Togashi from the ''[[Chunibyo]]'' series, Ken Washio in ''[[Science Ninja Team Gatchaman|Gatchaman]]'', Takashi Komuro in ''[[Highschool of the Dead]]'', and Zed in ''[[Kiba (anime)|Kiba]]''.\n\n==Filmography==\n===Anime===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n!Year\n!Title\n!Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" |Notes\n! class=\"unsortable\" |Source\n|-\n|2012\n|''[[Kids on the Slope]]''\n|Additional Voices\n|\n|\n|-\n|2013\n|''[[Btooom!|Btooom]]''\n|Tsuneaki Ida\n|\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2013-11-08/sentai-filmworks-unveils-btooom-s-dub-cast|title=Sentai Filmworks Unveils Btooom!'s Dub Cast|work=Anime News Network|access-date=2017-06-17|language=en}}</ref>\n|-\n|2015\n|''[[Chaika - The Coffin Princess]]'' series\n|Toru Acura\n|also season 2\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2015-11-03/chaika-the-coffin-princess-english-dub-casts-leraldo-anzaldua-as-toru/.94974|title=Chaika The Coffin Princess' English Dub Casts Leraldo Anzaldua as Toru|work=Anime News Network|access-date=2017-06-17|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.sentaifilmworks.com/news/chaika-the-coffin-princess-avenging-battle-english-dub-cast-list|title=Chaika the Coffin Princess: Avenging Battle English Dub Cast List|work=Sentai Filmworks|access-date=2017-06-17}}</ref>\n|-\n|2006\n|''[[Comic Party Revolution]]''